CAMPER × ISSEY MIYAKE
"Peu Form"

From Friday, July 11, a limited-time event has been held at StandBy in Omotesando to celebrate the launch. 

On the opening day, dancer and choreographer Mariko Kakizaki gave a performance set to music composed by Koki Nakano, a composer and pianist based in France.

StandBy
July 11ーJuly 20, 2025

7月11日（金）から、表参道のStandByで、CAMPER × ISSEY MIYAKE「Peu Form」の発売を記念した期間限定イベントを開催しています。
初日には、ダンサー・振付家の柿崎麻莉子氏が、フランスを拠点にする作曲家・ピアニスト中野公揮氏ご提供の楽曲に乗せて、パフォーマンスを行いました。

Ahead of the launch, a limited-time event is held at StandBy in Omotesando from Friday, July 11. On the opening day, dancer and choreographer Mariko Kakizaki gave a performance set to music composed by Koki Nakano, a composer and pianist based in France.

CAMPER × ISSEY MIYAKE
"Peu Form"

ISSEY MIYAKE is pleased to announce Peu Form, our first footwear project in collaboration with Camper. This partnership brings together two brands, each with 50 years of history and expertise, in a new initiative aimed at reasserting the value of handwork in everyday life and creating shoes that combine creative ideas with functionality.

カンペール社との協業による最初のフットウェア企画、Peu Formを発表します。このパートナーシップは、互いに50年の歴史と知識を擁する二つのブランドが、日々の暮らしの中に手仕事の価値を改めて提唱し、独創的な発想と機能性を兼ね備えた靴づくりを目指す新しい取組みです。
